1. Does it stack with Cantata (55)? No.  This song (just like the AE Manasong) gives 12mana/tick.  If the Bard is 60 that makes it 13mana/tick.  If that Bard also has level 3 Jamfest (Thott is currently the only known Bard with that) it gives 14mana/tick - the same as Kodiac.<br>
2. Does it stack with Manasong (32)? Yes.  This song gives 7mana/tick.   Jumps up to 12mana/tick if the Bard has their epic or twists in Amplification (30).  Jumps yet again up to 17mana/tick if the Bard uses Amplification AND has their epic.<br>
<br>
You can have up to 5 Bard singing #2 to you, as well.  And it all stacks. <p><img border="0" src=http://sleinad.homestead.com/files/puppetmaster11.jpg><br>
